                        <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11726WaldaIy">Walda ʾIyasus</persName>
                        <desc>
                           Written in the same hand as <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet104">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 104</ref> and <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet105">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 105</ref>. 
